        <mxCell id="6MimTV4tB0RpQHZ1C2n4-11" value="append to previous token" style="edgeLabel;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;fontSize=13;" vertex="1" connectable="0" parent="6MimTV4tB0RpQHZ1C2n4-10">
          <mxGeometry x="0.7501" y="2" relative="1" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint y="-1" as="offset" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="6MimTV4tB0RpQHZ1C2n4-9" value="Predicted Token" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;fontSize=13;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="3760" y="-424" width="60" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="6MimTV4tB0RpQHZ1C2n4-12" value="&lt;font&gt;Note: The Key &amp;amp; Value matrices computed&amp;nbsp; once need not be computed every time&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;rather they are stored in cache and reused accordingly&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;fontSize=13;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="30" y="50" width="540" height="20" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="6MimTV4tB0RpQHZ1C2n4-13" value="KV Cache" style="shape=cylinder3;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;boundedLbl=1;backgroundOutline=1;size=15;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;fontSize=13;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="270" y="140" width="60" height="80" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="6MimTV4tB0RpQHZ1C2n4-14" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=0;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;entryPerimeter=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;fontSize=13;" edge="1" parent="1" source="6MimTV4tB0RpQHZ1C2n4-12" target="6MimTV4tB0RpQHZ1C2n4-13">
          <mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="6MimTV4tB0RpQHZ1C2n4-15" value="KV Cache comprises of blocks" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;fontSize=13;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="50" y="165" width="180" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="6MimTV4tB0RpQHZ1C2n4-16" value="&lt;span&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: start;&quot;&gt;Prefill&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;— The model reads your entire prompt&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: start;&quot;&gt;in parallel&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;(all tokens at once) and builds the KV Cache. No output is generated yet. This is a compute-bound, one-shot operation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Self-attention is run across all token positions at once. Each token attends to every other. Keys and Values are computed and saved.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;All 4 input tokens have their Keys and Values cached. Prefill is complete. The model is now ready to start generating output tokens.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;fontSize=13;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="361" y="120" width="423.5" height="170" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="6MimTV4tB0RpQHZ1C2n4-17" value="&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: start;&quot;&gt;Decode&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;— The model generates tokens&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: start;&quot;&gt;one at a time&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;, auto-regressively. Each new token is appended to the KV Cache and fed back in. This is memory-bandwidth-bound and sequential.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Next token &quot;&amp;lt;Token&amp;gt;&quot; was just sampled from the output probability distribution. It is appended to the KV Cache and fed back as input. The model now predicts next token.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;fontSize=13;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="825.38" y="120" width="514.62" height="100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="6MimTV4tB0RpQHZ1C2n4-19" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: start; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(128, 170, 221);&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Prefill&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: start; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;• All input tokens processed together&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;• Compute-bound (GPU math)&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;• KV Cache written from scratch&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;• No output, just caching&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;• Scales O(n²) with prompt length&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;fontSize=13;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="420" y="310" width="320" height="180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="6MimTV4tB0RpQHZ1C2n4-20" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: start; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(122, 185, 72);&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Decode&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: start; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.7;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;• One token generated per step&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;• Memory-bandwidth-bound&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;• KV Cache grows with each token&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;• Output produced token by token&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;• Bottleneck for long generation&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontFamily=Comic Sans MS;fontSize=13;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="920" y="320" width="340" height="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
